{"title":"自由古巴万岁！","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":4,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由古巴万岁！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴呵，马蒂的母亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴呵，英雄的心灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀着何等的热情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热血在血管里奔腾；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“自由坚强的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比朝阳更加光明”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸膛挺在浪涛中间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像绿宝石一样晶莹；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼中燃烧着战斗决心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像苍空辉耀的晨星；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那折不断的手臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像棕榈树一样坚硬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——前进吧，古巴人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴又吹起号声！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——前进吧，古巴人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卡斯特罗发出雷鸣；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要用铁与火回击敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫工厂土地和母亲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万恶的兀鹰嗜血成性，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想把古巴一手扼死，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丑恶的脸卑污的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沾满了古巴的血腥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴呵，拉丁美洲的哨兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绝不允许强盗挑衅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大风暴又一次来临，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"响过马埃斯特腊的山顶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这是对暴君和敌寇的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不共戴天的仇恨”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要和恶魔决一死战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把瘟神赶下泥坑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由正义的火炬常明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的古巴人必胜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战斗的旗帜旁边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站着全世界的人民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听见莫斯科在说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定要作古巴的后盾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听见拉丁美洲在说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要为你拿出枪炮、生命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的大地和人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也在为你发出呼声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴呵，我们的青春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴呵，马蒂的亲人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将要披上红色的衣襟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远捧起绿叶与红星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——前进吧，古巴人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自由的古巴，必胜！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}